      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm absolutely in love with this car, but it's time for it to find a new home. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every single service milestone. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! I'm happy to answer any questions, so just give me a shout! \u2728",
