    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, having undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including VAC Motorsports rod bearings, a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, while the M-Variable limited-slip differential ensures precise torque distribution. The chassis remains tight with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, preserving the iconic handling and steering feedback of the E46 platform. A turn-key specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
