      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in true collector-grade condition, this vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional multi-stage ceramic coating with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and every piece of switchgear retains its factory-crisp tactile response. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. There are no leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched original floor mats, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a showroom-quality masterpiece that drives exactly as it did on day one.",
